    "type": "text",
    "content": "## 方案 B：完全在系统终端里跑，不依赖 Trae"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "如果你希望 实盘和 IDE 完全解耦 （比如 IDE 崩了、你换编辑器都无所谓），可以这样做："
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "1. 打开 Mac 自带的终端（Terminal 或 iTerm2 都行）；"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "2. 进入项目根目录："
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "```"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "cd /Users/chuan/Desktop/xiangmu/客户端"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "```"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "3. 激活虚拟环境（如果有 Quant_Unified/.venv ）："
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "```"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "source Quant_Unified/.venv/bin/activate"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "```"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "4. 启动 2 号实盘脚本："
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "```"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "python -X utf8 Quant_Unified/strategies/"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "二号网格策略/real_trading.py"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "```"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "5. 另开一个终端窗口（或标签），用刚才说的："
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "```"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "cd /Users/chuan/Desktop/xiangmu/客户端/"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "Quant_Unified"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "tail -f logs/grid_strategy_live.log"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "```"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "这样一来："
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "- 实盘完全跑在 系统终端 里；"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "- Trae IDE 只是一个编辑器，你关不关它，对实盘和日志文件都没影响；"
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "content": "- 日志你可以随时在任意终端里 tail -f 出来看。"
  },
